name: ꌗ ꀎ ꈤ ꀸ ꍏ ꌩ х ["WEEKLY TIREDNESS" collection]
description: This feeling is painful, but it appears when we feel tiredeness after a hard week. That's why we try not to think about anything. Just want to freeze all. Stop motion. 1 section - 1 day of the week, which contains something. It was. It is. And it will be today. But exhaustion will eat every day, it will be pleasant or not, physical or mental. There are people who yearn for immortality, but do not know what they will do if it rains on Sunday. :: Size :: 1700*2000 | 300 dpi :: handwork ::
